<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3737.1.5>
    dc:creator "Carrejo, Nancy; Diaz, Ana E.; Woodley, Norman E." ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Lixophaga Townsend (Diptera: Tachinidae) from Colombia, a parasitoid of Neoleucinodes elegantalis (Guenée) (Lepidoptera: Crambidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219400>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219401>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219402>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219403> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219400>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Male of LixoPhaga Puscolulo Carrejo & Woodley, sp. nov. 1. Dorsal view. 2. Lateral view of head and anterior part of thorax, right side. 3. Lateral view, right side. 4. Anterior view of head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219401>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 8. Female of LixoPhaga Puscolulo Carrejo & Woodley, sp. nov. 5. Lateral view, right side. 6. Lateral view of head and anterior part of thorax, right side. 7. Dorsal view. 8. Anterior view of head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219402>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 10. Male terminalia of LixoPhaga Puscolulo Carrejo & Woodley, sp. nov. (slide mounted). 9. Lateral view of right side. 10. Posterior view of cerci and surstyli from slide mounted specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219402/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219403>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 14. Host and immature stages of LixoPhaga Puscolulo Carrejo & Woodley, sp. nov. 11. Larva of Neoleucinodes elegantalis parasitized by LixoPhaga Puscolulo. Dark spots are parasitism symptoms observed on the body of the host larva. 12. Third instar larva of LixoPhaga Puscolulo abandoning its host larva. 13. Prepupa of LixoPhaga Puscolulo. 14. Puparium of LixoPhaga Puscolulo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219403/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

